WEBVTT

00:02:57.000 --> 00:03:01.893
to use the viruses
themselves as therapies --

00:03:01.917 --> 00:03:04.643
as building blocks for therapies.

00:03:04.667 --> 00:03:09.125
To build therapies
that could mutate and transmit.

00:03:09.958 --> 00:03:12.726
Let me share with you
how we've had a major breakthrough,

00:03:12.750 --> 00:03:16.042
and we're already testing
these new therapies.

00:03:18.417 --> 00:03:23.750
HIV is the most devastating
pandemic of our era.

00:03:24.625 --> 00:03:26.268
75 million infected;

00:03:26.292 --> 00:03:27.875
33 million dead.

00:03:29.250 --> 00:03:32.684
Most of us think
that HIV is a solved problem.